title: Bug 4121: JarExporter causes out of Sync
description: The JarExporter (1GILQD5) is causing the application to go out of sync.
OB: When using the JarExporter, the exported jar file includes itself.
EB: The exported jar file should not include itself to avoid causing the application to go out of sync.
SR:
To reproduce the issue:
1. Use the JarExporter to export a jar file.
2. Examine the contents of the exported jar file and verify if it includes itself.
